=== LIFE_POD_CLUSTER ===
# id: 87
# title: The Life Pod Cluster
# chinese_title: 救生舱群
# category: Wreckage
# mode: dungeon

A cluster of escape pods has drifted together, their magnetic clamps locking them into a makeshift raft. Most are empty, their occupants long since rescued or lost. One pod's status light still blinks amber — it may contain supplies or a stasis occupant.

* [Open the amber-lit pod]
  ~ gain_radical("人")
  "生" (shēng) — life, to live, to be born
* [Strip the empty pods for components]
  ~ gain_gold(20)
  "空" (kōng) — empty, hollow
* [Check the pod cluster's distress beacon]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "求" (qiú) — to seek, to request help
* [Use a pod as temporary shelter to rest]
  ~ heal(15)
  "休" (xiū) — to rest, to stop
